attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Premier Realty Lake Minnetonka

data.description: Quaint story and a half 3 bedroom, 1 bath home located in the heart of Delano. Home features a recently remodeled kitchen, main floor laundry, and a main level bedroom. There are also 2+ bedrooms upstairs with another bonus room that could be used as a bedroom but does not have a closet, and another unfinished area that could be another bedroom/bathroom. This home has beautiful flower gardens with raised garden beds as well. Also features a new metal roof.
